1
00:01:43,080 --> 00:01:45,000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

2
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:53,360
I don't usually drink much.

3
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:55,040
-So-- -Who did you go with?

4
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:59,320
My roommates.

5
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,800
They were all people I know.

6
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:01,920
Roommates?

7
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:04,280
What about the guy who came out with you yesterday?

8
00:02:04,360 --> 00:02:05,800
The one who is 195 cm tall

9
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:07,920
and just gave you a hamburger.

10
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,360
Is he also your roommate?

11
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:13,760
No, that is my roommate's boyfriend's friend.

12
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,680
Is that him?

13
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:20,560
What do you mean?

14
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:22,960
The guy you like.

15
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,680
Is it him?

16
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,400
Is he?

17
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:36,040
No.

18
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,160
No?

19
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:40,080
So tell me.

20
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:42,040
If that isn't your type, what is?

21
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,000
I don't want to.

22
00:02:49,880 --> 00:02:50,880
Jiaxu.

23
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:53,360
-The bubble-- -Is it a guy who is cute

24
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,200
and delicate-looking?

25
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,400
No.

26
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:03,200
He…

27
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:05,800
He's manly.

28
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:08,560
Manly?

29
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,360
So…

30
00:03:13,600 --> 00:03:14,760
You like

31
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,240
muscular guys.

32
00:03:19,760 --> 00:03:20,600
Is that it?

33
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,200
No.

34
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:27,920
No muscles but is manly.

35
00:03:28,640 --> 00:03:30,360
Also, he's nice to everyone.

36
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,440
But the guy you described

37
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,840
sounds like a jerk.

38
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:35,920
He's not a jerk.

39
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,680
-He is. -He isn't.

40
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:40,920
You're so nosy.

41
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,040
I'm nosy?

42
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:45,160
I've never met a guy like that in my life.

43
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,320
-Gosh. -I'm just curious.

44
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:48,440
You're so nosy.

45
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,640
Can you stop asking?

46
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,200
Fine.

47
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:52,640
I won't ask anymore.

48
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,440
If you're curious,

49
00:03:56,160 --> 00:03:58,160
just look in the mirror.

50
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:05,880
Jiaxu.

51
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:08,440
Yes?

52
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,440
You…

53
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:12,800
You're in your twenties now.

54
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:14,520
Why don't you get a girlfriend

55
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,079
instead of bothering me--

56
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,519
Where would I get a girlfriend?

57
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,079
Why don't you

58
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:22,200
introduce one to me?

59
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:25,440
That won't do.

60
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,920
I only know girls around my age.

61
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,280
Around your age?

62
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,720
I'm fine with that.

63
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,480
What do you mean?

64
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:46,600
The literal meaning.

65
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:56,600
Is he teasing me?

66
00:04:58,200 --> 00:05:01,200
He has never said something like this to me before.

67
00:05:27,520 --> 00:05:28,760
Pull over.

68
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,080
Mom!

69
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:34,760
Zhizhi.

70
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:35,680
Zhizhi!

71
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,320
I've missed you so much.

72
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:41,360
You're finally home.

73
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:43,200
What took so long? Was the flight delayed?

74
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:44,840
No.

75
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,280
It was Sang Yan.

76
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:48,840
Sang Yan made me wait at the airport for so long.

77
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:50,120
Why?

78
00:05:50,200 --> 00:05:51,840
Why did you make Zhizhi wait?

79
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,440
No, Mom. You told me to buy

80
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:55,480
her favorite crispy taro-crusted duck.

81
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:57,000
-Yes. -I was in line for half an hour.

82
00:05:57,080 --> 00:05:58,360
You should've gone earlier.

83
00:05:58,440 --> 00:06:00,520
-That's right. -You made her wait alone.

84
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,520
That was so dangerous.

85
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:03,720
My sweetheart. You've lost weight.

86
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:04,760
I haven't.

87
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:06,440
I made your favorite dish. What is it?

88
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:07,800
-Steamed fish. -Not only that.

89
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:09,360
-I bought strawberries. -Strawberries?

90
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:10,480
Big strawberries!

91
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:12,960
-White strawberries. -Bring the luggage in.

92
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:14,440
-I… -Bring it all in.

93
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:17,960
When the little princess comes home,

94
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,200
I'm just a helper.

95
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:21,440
The door!

96
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:32,400
The little princess is home.

97
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:40,800
Mom.

98
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:42,920
Your New Year's gift.

99
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:43,960
You bought it for me?

100
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:46,160
You'll like it. Open it.

101
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,040
Careful, this is hot.

102
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:49,920
Is this it?

103
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:50,960
Yes.

104
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:52,040
And this too.

105
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,200
You bought two.

106
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,960
I saved up for a long while.

107
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:55,960
Thank you so much.

108
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:59,840
Dad, this is your New Year's gift.

109
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:01,840
-Thank you. -It's hand cream.

110
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:04,040
Use it when you go to construction sites.

111
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:06,360
Then your hands won't get chapped during winter.

112
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:07,520
Thank you, Zhizhi.

113
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:09,640
-Good girl. -She is so considerate.

114
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,480
-I've grown up. -Only she would think of this.

115
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:12,720
I've become mature.

116
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:14,120
Thank you.
Don't worry about me.

117
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:17,280
-Don't worry. -You give her too much allowance.

118
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,840
Stop funding her next semester.

119
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:20,280
Where is mine?

120
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:24,120
That's more like it.

121
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:25,160
It looks great.

122
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:26,960
-Really? -Super cool.

123
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,480
Mom, look at him.

124
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:29,440
Isn't it?

125
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:32,160
-What's wrong? -What is this? I don't want it. Take it.

126
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,800
Why not?

127
00:07:33,880 --> 00:07:36,040
-It looks ugly. -It's not.

128
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,840
I don't like it!

129
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,480
Dad, does this look good to you?

130
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:40,400
It's stupid.

131
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:42,920
It's nice.

132
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:45,040
I know you have a fine taste.

133
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:48,680
Asymmetric glasses are trendy this year.

134
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:50,480
-Don't you like it? -No, I don't.

135
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:52,520
-No? -No.

136
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,640
-No? -No!

137
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,560
Say you like it!

138
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,800
I like it!

139
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:58,160
Say you like it wholeheartedly.

140
00:07:58,240 --> 00:08:00,080
I wholeheartedly don't like it!

141
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:02,920
-Then don't wear it. -That's enough. I love this liveliness.

142
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:04,240
Eat this.

143
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:05,840
-Sit. -Doesn't it taste good?

144
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:10,000
Little demon.

145
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:11,080
Let me tell you.

146
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:13,160
I waited in line for half an hour

147
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:15,400
to buy this crispy taro-crusted duck.

148
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:17,600
You had better eat it and…

149
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:19,120
Thank you, Sang Yan.

150
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:20,840
Give my glasses back to me.

151
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:22,680
I'll take them since they're free.

152
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:33,360
Does it taste good?

153
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:36,000
Zhizhi.

154
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:38,159
Last time, you told me

155
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,640
that Xiaoduan had appendicitis.

156
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,280
How is he now?

157
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,480
He has recovered well.

158
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:46,640
The doctor said it was caused by irregular meal timings.

159
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:48,200
He didn't eat properly.

160
00:08:48,280 --> 00:08:49,280
So you heard that too.

161
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:50,280
You mustn't skip meals.

162
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:53,400
He had a tough life before.

163
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,440
He was often working.

164
00:08:54,520 --> 00:08:56,800
That probably impacted his health.

165
00:08:56,880 --> 00:08:58,000
How is he doing at work now?

166
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:01,360
Pretty well.

167
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:03,960
Many of my classmates know about the game he designed.

168
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:05,600
It's very popular.

169
00:09:05,680 --> 00:09:06,800
That's good to hear.

170
00:09:06,880 --> 00:09:08,560
The boy is pretty good.

171
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:12,360
Look at Sang Yan. He looks dumb.

172
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:19,280
Listen, Sang Yan.

173
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,400
Look at Xiaoduan,

174
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,360
then look at yourself.

175
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:25,080
I set up a meeting for you and Mrs. Zhang's daughter.

176
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:27,640
She waited for you all afternoon and you didn't show up.

177
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,440
I told you.

178
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:31,760
I wouldn't go.

179
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:34,080
I set it up for you. Why didn't you go?

180
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:36,360
You should've turned up out of courtesy

181
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,800
and met with her.

182
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:39,440
Dad, Mom.

183
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:42,000
Do I look like I need that?

184
00:09:43,040 --> 00:09:44,320
Absolutely not.

185
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:45,840
So stop setting up meetings.

186
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:47,280
I won't go.

187
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,360
Was it a blind date?

188
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:52,880
Fine.

189
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:55,800
I've poked my meddling nose.

190
00:09:56,520 --> 00:09:58,920
You're always doing nothing all day.

191
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,800
I thought you would have time for tea.

192
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:04,760
I didn't know you were so busy.

193
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,000
That was close.

194
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,200
You're so stubborn.

195
00:10:10,280 --> 00:10:11,440
You'll end up old and alone.

196
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:16,320
Enough. Don't waste the strawberries.

197
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:18,360
I find that we've lost our dynamic.

198
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,520
I'll toss one. Open wide.

199
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,640
Don't waste the strawberries.

200
00:10:22,680 --> 00:10:25,040
-Zhizhi, this steamed fish is for you. -I'll toss the bowl.

201
00:10:25,680 --> 00:10:27,640
Zhizhi, I made this steamed fish for you.

202
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:29,120
Hurry and eat.

203
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:30,240
Come on. It will get cold.

204
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:31,240
-Okay. -Hurry and eat.
Come on.

205
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:44,200
I don't need this. Put it back.

206
00:10:44,680 --> 00:10:45,560
I don't need this!

207
00:10:49,920 --> 00:10:51,200
Are you trying to kill me?

208
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,680
Put it away.

209
00:10:58,800 --> 00:10:59,680
What's wrong with you?

210
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:01,600
You must want something.

211
00:11:07,160 --> 00:11:09,760
Are you going on blind dates?

212
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:11,520
Why do you care?

213
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:17,320
No wonder you're suddenly so kind to me.

214
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:22,560
So did you not go on that blind date?

215
00:11:24,800 --> 00:11:27,320
Do you think I need to go on a blind date?

216
00:11:27,880 --> 00:11:29,480
Don't you need to?

217
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:32,200
What will you do with the rest of your life

218
00:11:32,280 --> 00:11:33,760
if you don't go on blind dates?

219
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:40,000
Was it because you felt embarrassed to go?

220
00:11:41,040 --> 00:11:42,640
If you do feel that way,

221
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:43,720
you can

222
00:11:44,800 --> 00:11:46,520
ask Duan Jiaxu to go with you.

223
00:11:54,920 --> 00:11:56,520
Take him with you.

224
00:11:57,480 --> 00:11:58,640
You're single.

225
00:11:58,720 --> 00:12:00,240
He's one year older than you

226
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:01,640
and he's single too.

227
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:02,760
Besides…

228
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:05,680
Besides, I think he may

229
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:09,720
want a girlfriend now.

230
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:11,920
Maybe you can go to him in Yihe.

231
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:15,000
Or he can come to you in Nanwu.

232
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,600
You two can go together.

233
00:12:16,680 --> 00:12:18,560
Then you won't feel embarrassed.

234
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:24,200
Why?

235
00:12:24,280 --> 00:12:25,760
Did Duan Jiaxu get on your wrong side?

236
00:12:26,680 --> 00:12:27,640
I just think

237
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:30,120
that he's not young anymore.

238
00:12:30,680 --> 00:12:32,760
If he doesn't find a girlfriend, he might

239
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:34,640
end up being pathetically alone.

240
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:37,400
If he ends up pathetically alone,

241
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:38,760
that's his business.

242
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:41,160
Don't compare me with him.

243
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:45,200
So are you going on blind dates or not?

244
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:46,120
I don't need to.

245
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,840
In that case…

246
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:53,320
But Mom told you to go.

247
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:00,280
Do you know why?

248
00:13:03,400 --> 00:13:04,840
Because there's a girl

249
00:13:04,920 --> 00:13:06,320
trying to pursue me right now.

250
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:07,360
Got it?

251
00:13:16,640 --> 00:13:18,160
What's with that look? I mean it.

252
00:13:18,920 --> 00:13:19,880
So…

253
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:23,000
You can tell Duan Jiaxu

254
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:24,800
to go alone

255
00:13:25,560 --> 00:13:28,280
and enjoy the blind date

256
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:31,760
with his tacky pickup lines.

257
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:36,520
Open the gate.

258
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:37,640
Open it.

259
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:38,680
Climb over it.

260
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:43,400
Open the gate! You're so childish!

261
00:13:43,480 --> 00:13:44,840
Call me handsome. Come on.

262
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:47,560
Do it.

263
00:13:50,800 --> 00:13:51,640
You're handsome.

264
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:52,880
Louder.

265
00:13:53,880 --> 00:13:54,880
You're handsome.

266
00:13:55,520 --> 00:13:56,400
Even louder.

267
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:58,120
What's wrong with you?

268
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:01,720
You're handsome. Open the gate now.

269
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:03,720
That's the way.

270
00:14:05,520 --> 00:14:06,600
You're a good sister.

271
00:14:06,680 --> 00:14:07,520
Please.

272
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:08,680
Handsome, my foot.

273
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:15,360
Hey!

274
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:16,680
I have to go out later.

275
00:14:19,800 --> 00:14:20,640
Mom!

276
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:22,520
Mom!

277
00:14:25,040 --> 00:14:26,040
Zhizhi, smell this.

278
00:14:26,120 --> 00:14:27,680
Does it smell like the sun?

279
00:14:27,760 --> 00:14:29,200
Why would it smell like the sun?

280
00:14:29,280 --> 00:14:31,520
I've sunned the quilt all day.

281
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:36,080
That's why I'm just making the bed now.

282
00:14:36,160 --> 00:14:37,040
All right.

283
00:14:37,120 --> 00:14:39,160
Go and get the teddy bear blanket.

284
00:14:40,920 --> 00:14:42,040
Is it still in the cabinet?

285
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:43,440
Yes, it's in there.

286
00:14:43,520 --> 00:14:44,360
Okay.

287
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:59,160
-Found it? -Yes.

288
00:15:04,160 --> 00:15:05,960
- I'll put it here. -I'll do it.

289
00:15:06,040 --> 00:15:07,600
Mom, go and get some rest.

290
00:15:07,680 --> 00:15:08,520
It's late now.

291
00:15:08,600 --> 00:15:10,280
-Good night. -Good night.

292
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:12,040
All right. I'll go and wash this first.

293
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:13,520
-Go ahead. -Okay. Good night.

294
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:14,920
-Bye. -Bye.

295
00:16:04,400 --> 00:16:06,400
SANG ZHI, HAPPY 18TH BIRTHDAY

296
00:16:08,120 --> 00:16:11,440
SANG ZHI, HAPPY 18TH BIRTHDAY

297
00:16:23,640 --> 00:16:24,960
Where would I get a girlfriend?

298
00:16:25,800 --> 00:16:26,960
Why don't you

299
00:16:27,040 --> 00:16:28,320
introduce one to me?

300
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:32,000
That won't do.

301
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:34,000
I only know girls around my age.

302
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:36,560
Around your age?

303
00:16:38,800 --> 00:16:39,920
I'm fine with that.

304
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:42,840
Is he serious about that?

305
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:00,080
SANG ZHI
Jiaxu.

306
00:17:01,920 --> 00:17:03,920
I think Sang Yan has a girlfriend.

307
00:17:06,720 --> 00:17:07,640
Really?

308
00:17:07,720 --> 00:17:09,359
BROTHER NO. 2

309
00:17:11,520 --> 00:17:14,760
I think she's a younger girl.

310
00:17:15,520 --> 00:17:16,839
SANG ZHI

311
00:17:20,800 --> 00:17:23,040
Don't tell me he likes a minor.

312
00:17:26,800 --> 00:17:28,359
Is it fine as long as she's an adult?

313
00:17:40,040 --> 00:17:42,440
An adult would be in college.

314
00:17:42,520 --> 00:17:43,920
Doesn't that make her a grown-up?

315
00:17:46,320 --> 00:17:47,400
So why not?

316
00:17:58,920 --> 00:18:02,880
She's only asking about Sang Yan, right?

317
00:18:06,280 --> 00:18:09,000
It's acceptable when it happens to someone else.

318
00:18:09,920 --> 00:18:11,560
But if it were to happen to herself,

319
00:18:12,120 --> 00:18:13,960
she would probably find it hard to accept.

320
00:18:15,040 --> 00:18:16,400
After all, to her,

321
00:18:17,040 --> 00:18:18,480
I'm just a big brother.

322
00:18:23,040 --> 00:18:25,120
Had we not met each other until now,

323
00:18:25,200 --> 00:18:27,320
I at 19 and he at 24,

324
00:18:28,840 --> 00:18:31,560
he would've seen me as a peer.

325
00:18:33,680 --> 00:18:35,240
Sadly, that didn't happen.

326
00:18:36,640 --> 00:18:37,880
Perhaps in his eyes,

327
00:18:39,640 --> 00:18:41,360
I will always be a 14-year-old girl

328
00:18:43,600 --> 00:18:45,760
who is just his good friend's sister.

329
00:18:47,120 --> 00:18:52,800
DON'T TELL ME HE LIKES A MINOR. IS IT FINE AS LONG AS SHE'S AN ADULT?

330
00:19:09,040 --> 00:19:11,480
CHAPTER 13, FEEL YOU OUT

331
00:19:11,560 --> 00:19:13,800
I'M GUESSING YOU'RE FALLING TOO

332
00:19:17,200 --> 00:19:18,920
I've been busy planning my wedding

333
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:20,560
and also had to come to Yihe for work.

334
00:19:21,040 --> 00:19:22,040
If you hadn't called me,

335
00:19:22,120 --> 00:19:23,600
I wouldn't have had much to eat today.

336
00:19:24,160 --> 00:19:25,560
Then eat more.

337
00:19:25,640 --> 00:19:26,720
Order more if you want.

338
00:19:27,560 --> 00:19:28,800
I won't hold back with you.

339
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:32,880
Listen, Duan Jiaxu.

340
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:36,600
I won't ask you and Sang Yan to be my groomsmen.

341
00:19:37,440 --> 00:19:39,320
Why? Do you have a problem with me?

342
00:19:39,920 --> 00:19:41,680
I have a problem with you and Sang Yan.

343
00:19:41,760 --> 00:19:43,000
Picture my wedding.

344
00:19:43,080 --> 00:19:44,800
If you, Sang Yan, and I

345
00:19:44,880 --> 00:19:45,800
are standing together,

346
00:19:45,880 --> 00:19:48,000
people might think you're there to steal my bride.

347
00:19:48,880 --> 00:19:50,480
That's nonsensical.

348
00:19:51,760 --> 00:19:52,600
Duan Jiaxu.

349
00:19:52,680 --> 00:19:54,560
We haven't talked much on the phone lately.

350
00:19:54,640 --> 00:19:56,120
Why haven't you contacted me?

351
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:57,640
What has been keeping you busy?

352
00:19:57,720 --> 00:19:59,720
What else but work?

353
00:20:02,360 --> 00:20:04,760
You haven't mentioned the girl you like lately.

354
00:20:05,360 --> 00:20:06,240
Let's talk about it.

355
00:20:06,760 --> 00:20:08,080
Nothing has happened.

356
00:20:08,160 --> 00:20:09,400
There isn't much to talk about.

357
00:20:09,480 --> 00:20:11,440
Don't keep mum. Tell me. I'm so curious.

358
00:20:11,520 --> 00:20:13,400
Please. What kind of girl is she?

359
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:18,200
She's a young lady.

360
00:20:18,280 --> 00:20:19,400
She's a bit younger.

361
00:20:20,840 --> 00:20:22,080
You don't know her.

362
00:20:22,160 --> 00:20:23,320
What's wrong with being young

363
00:20:23,400 --> 00:20:24,800
so long as she isn't a minor?

364
00:20:24,880 --> 00:20:26,640
Pursue her if she's of legal age

365
00:20:26,720 --> 00:20:27,800
or I'll look down on you.

366
00:20:28,520 --> 00:20:29,640
It's not like that.

367
00:20:31,520 --> 00:20:33,560
I feel somewhat guilty about it.

368
00:20:34,120 --> 00:20:36,640
Guilty? Aren't you worried that she'll get taken?

369
00:20:37,480 --> 00:20:38,680
That's normal.

370
00:20:39,800 --> 00:20:41,560
If she meets a good guy,

371
00:20:41,640 --> 00:20:42,800
I'll be happy for her.

372
00:20:44,120 --> 00:20:45,440
Does that mean

373
00:20:45,520 --> 00:20:46,800
she has someone she likes?

374
00:20:50,800 --> 00:20:52,680
This girl is impressive

375
00:20:52,760 --> 00:20:54,160
to take no interest in you.

376
00:20:54,760 --> 00:20:55,920
Duan Jiaxu, don't be sad.

377
00:20:56,000 --> 00:20:57,560
What kind of guy does she like?

378
00:20:57,640 --> 00:20:59,560
I'll analyze it and give you advice. Tell me.

379
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:04,160
Well, this guy

380
00:21:04,800 --> 00:21:05,760
is quite a flirt.

381
00:21:06,280 --> 00:21:07,920
He is a ladies' man and nice to everyone.

382
00:21:08,800 --> 00:21:10,680
He might even be a bit shameless.

383
00:21:11,520 --> 00:21:12,360
Isn't that you?

384
00:21:14,120 --> 00:21:15,280
Are you insulting me?

385
00:21:15,360 --> 00:21:16,240
No.

386
00:21:16,920 --> 00:21:18,240
Is there any chance

387
00:21:18,320 --> 00:21:19,560
that she's talking about you?

388
00:21:20,320 --> 00:21:21,640
Impossible.

389
00:21:21,720 --> 00:21:23,040
I've met that guy before.

390
00:21:23,120 --> 00:21:25,240
His image fits her description quite well.

391
00:21:25,880 --> 00:21:27,240
He's quite flirty.

392
00:21:27,320 --> 00:21:28,680
He's just a jerk.

393
00:21:29,720 --> 00:21:30,920
Maybe not.

394
00:21:31,640 --> 00:21:33,920
You see, one speaks contrary to their mind

395
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:35,560
in front of their crush.

396
00:21:35,640 --> 00:21:37,320
When I was in college, I chased a girl,

397
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:38,960
Wan Ling in Foreign Languages.

398
00:21:39,040 --> 00:21:40,720
I was her rebound when she had a breakup.

399
00:21:40,800 --> 00:21:42,480
When they got back together, she told me,

400
00:21:43,240 --> 00:21:45,360
"Qian Fei, what kind of girl do you like?

401
00:21:45,440 --> 00:21:46,640
I can introduce one to you."

402
00:21:46,720 --> 00:21:48,480
What could I say to her?

403
00:21:48,560 --> 00:21:50,520
I simply made up someone based on her.

404
00:21:51,800 --> 00:21:54,120
You made up a girl based on her?

405
00:21:58,400 --> 00:21:59,600
It's not very likely.

406
00:22:03,200 --> 00:22:05,080
But it's possible.

407
00:22:06,120 --> 00:22:07,280
Right?

408
00:22:08,160 --> 00:22:09,960
Listen, I swear to you.

409
00:22:10,040 --> 00:22:12,680
I haven't met many guys who fit that description better than you do.

410
00:22:16,080 --> 00:22:17,240
Miss, I want to order more!

411
00:22:21,680 --> 00:22:24,600
Am I the guy she likes?

412
00:22:24,680 --> 00:22:26,160
Sir, what would you like to order?

413
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:27,800
-Chicken wings. -All right.

414
00:22:27,880 --> 00:22:29,440
-And this too. -Okay, right away.

415
00:22:46,320 --> 00:22:47,440
I've arrived in Nanwu.

416
00:22:47,520 --> 00:22:48,560
See you later.

417
00:22:55,400 --> 00:22:56,760
Okay.

418
00:22:59,320 --> 00:23:01,240
Why did he tell me this?

419
00:23:09,520 --> 00:23:11,160
-Do I leave the red packet here? -No need.

420
00:23:11,240 --> 00:23:12,320
They're waiting. Hurry over.

421
00:23:12,400 --> 00:23:13,640
-No? -It's fine.

422
00:23:13,720 --> 00:23:14,640
-Come on. -Let's go.

423
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:17,120
What took you so long today?

424
00:23:17,200 --> 00:23:18,200
The traffic was terrible.

425
00:23:18,280 --> 00:23:20,280
Listen, Qian Fei is really nervous.

426
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:26,400
Buddy!

427
00:23:26,480 --> 00:23:27,720
Did you put on weight?

428
00:23:27,800 --> 00:23:29,040
-A little. -Not much.

429
00:23:29,120 --> 00:23:30,080
Good, you're happy.

430
00:23:30,880 --> 00:23:33,000
-Hi, Sang Zhi. -Qian Fei.

431
00:23:33,520 --> 00:23:34,760
Congratulations.

432
00:23:36,080 --> 00:23:38,280
I stopped her from giving a red packet at the door.

433
00:23:38,360 --> 00:23:39,880
-You won't accept it, right? -Right.

434
00:23:39,960 --> 00:23:41,560
It's just a little something. Accept it.

435
00:23:41,640 --> 00:23:43,200
I can't. It's the thought that counts.

436
00:23:43,280 --> 00:23:44,160
No need for this.

437
00:23:44,240 --> 00:23:45,400
Please take it.

438
00:23:45,480 --> 00:23:46,600
No.

439
00:23:46,680 --> 00:23:48,600
You're so generous today.

440
00:23:48,680 --> 00:23:50,720
Am I? I expect two packets from you.

441
00:23:53,720 --> 00:23:55,320
Don't just drink by yourself.

442
00:23:55,400 --> 00:23:56,440
You and I are drinking

443
00:23:56,520 --> 00:23:57,920
after the wedding, all right?

444
00:23:58,400 --> 00:23:59,960
-Take your seats. -Right, come on.

445
00:24:00,040 --> 00:24:01,400
-You'll sit here. -Sit here.

446
00:24:01,480 --> 00:24:02,320
Let's go, Sang Zhi.

447
00:24:02,400 --> 00:24:03,440
-Sit. -Look after them.

448
00:24:03,520 --> 00:24:04,400
-You sit here. -Sit.

449
00:24:06,040 --> 00:24:07,520
If he doesn't want it, give it to me.

450
00:24:08,120 --> 00:24:09,160
Jiaxu!

451
00:24:09,240 --> 00:24:11,000
-Jiaxu, over here! -Over here.

452
00:24:11,080 --> 00:24:12,240
What took you so long?

453
00:24:12,320 --> 00:24:14,560
I was going in circles outside.

454
00:24:15,080 --> 00:24:16,800
You cleaned up nicely today.

455
00:24:16,880 --> 00:24:17,800
He's handsome, right?

456
00:24:17,880 --> 00:24:20,120
Hey, man. Do you know what time it is now?

457
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:21,520
You nearly missed my wedding.

458
00:24:23,280 --> 00:24:24,880
I was going in circles.

459
00:24:26,120 --> 00:24:28,440
-Okay, I'll go and get ready. -Isn't that the tie I gave him?

460
00:24:28,920 --> 00:24:30,080
Do your best.

461
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:31,400
-I'll get ready now. -Go ahead.

462
00:24:31,480 --> 00:24:32,560
-Sit there. -Leave it to me.

463
00:24:32,640 --> 00:24:34,200
-Come on, take a seat. -Sit.

464
00:24:39,440 --> 00:24:40,560
You're so well-dressed today.

465
00:24:41,920 --> 00:24:43,760
Jiaxu, say something nice.

466
00:24:43,840 --> 00:24:45,520
I'll give you a red packet for New Year.

467
00:24:47,760 --> 00:24:49,640
It's hard to say something nice about you.

468
00:24:50,960 --> 00:24:52,800
Why don't I call you "darling brother"?

469
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:53,720
Call me "brother."

470
00:24:53,800 --> 00:24:55,080
I'm fine with "brother."

471
00:24:57,320 --> 00:24:58,560
Darling brother.

472
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:03,440
Is he drunk already?

473
00:25:05,040 --> 00:25:06,280
Who are you trying to gross out?

474
00:25:06,360 --> 00:25:08,560
Jiaxu, you two have become grosser since university.

475
00:25:08,640 --> 00:25:10,080
Indeed.

476
00:25:10,160 --> 00:25:12,040
Darling brother, they're badmouthing me.

477
00:25:12,120 --> 00:25:12,960
Gross!

478
00:25:15,600 --> 00:25:16,720
This is mine now.

479
00:25:17,520 --> 00:25:18,400
Starting today,

480
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:21,000
Sang Yan is my darling brother.

481
00:25:21,600 --> 00:25:22,920
Are you insane?

482
00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:24,240
Sang Yan, give in. It's okay.

483
00:25:24,320 --> 00:25:25,160
Sure, okay.

484
00:25:25,240 --> 00:25:26,800
It makes me cringe.

485
00:25:26,880 --> 00:25:28,360
I've got goosebumps all over.

486
00:25:28,440 --> 00:25:30,200
-Let's drink. -Bottoms up.

487
00:25:30,280 --> 00:25:31,160
Brother.

488
00:25:31,920 --> 00:25:33,240
Don't call me that.

489
00:25:33,320 --> 00:25:34,640
Hearing that makes me sick now.

490
00:25:36,360 --> 00:25:37,280
Then…
What?

491
00:25:39,680 --> 00:25:40,840
Did something happen

492
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:43,200
to him?

493
00:25:43,280 --> 00:25:45,120
He seems weird today.

494
00:25:46,320 --> 00:25:47,960
I'll tell you what happened to him.

495
00:25:50,280 --> 00:25:51,440
Here.

496
00:25:51,520 --> 00:25:53,520
Yihe Psychiatric Hospital.

497
00:25:56,840 --> 00:25:58,360
Go straight there when you get back.

498
00:25:59,760 --> 00:26:01,240
Darling brother, you're so considerate

499
00:26:01,320 --> 00:26:02,800
to find a hospital for me.

500
00:26:02,880 --> 00:26:04,640
Man, stop calling me that. Okay?

501
00:26:04,720 --> 00:26:05,960
Why, my darling brother?

502
00:26:06,040 --> 00:26:08,360
Scoot over, Sang Zhi. Let's switch seats.

503
00:26:08,840 --> 00:26:10,960
I'm going to puke even before I drink.

504
00:26:11,040 --> 00:26:12,040
Sit over there.

505
00:26:12,120 --> 00:26:13,680
Okay? Please, I beg of you.

506
00:26:15,520 --> 00:26:16,760
What's wrong with you?

507
00:26:16,840 --> 00:26:18,120
Scoot over.

508
00:26:22,400 --> 00:26:24,360
-It has been a while! -Maybe for you two.

509
00:26:24,440 --> 00:26:25,640
We just met up last week!

510
00:26:27,400 --> 00:26:30,320
-Next, let's welcome our groom, -What should I say?

511
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:31,840
who's plump from love's nourishment,

512
00:26:31,920 --> 00:26:33,680
but still looks handsome,

513
00:26:33,760 --> 00:26:34,960
Qian Fei,

514
00:26:35,040 --> 00:26:37,520
and his beloved bride, Shiwen!

515
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:41,480
Let's welcome them to the stage!

516
00:26:45,800 --> 00:26:47,200
I wonder if the staircase

517
00:26:47,280 --> 00:26:49,320
can bear the weight of their love!

518
00:26:49,880 --> 00:26:51,480
Let's give them a round of applause!

519
00:26:55,120 --> 00:26:56,200
Come on, Feifei.

520
00:26:56,280 --> 00:26:58,000
Look at this sturdy staircase.

521
00:26:58,080 --> 00:26:59,880
It's like the path of their future.

522
00:26:59,960 --> 00:27:01,680
With each and every step they take,

523
00:27:01,760 --> 00:27:03,280
they walk their way to their happiness

524
00:27:03,360 --> 00:27:04,240
and stability.

525
00:27:04,320 --> 00:27:05,280
And this moment

526
00:27:05,360 --> 00:27:06,920
deserves cheering and applause

527
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:11,000
from all of you!

528
00:27:12,880 --> 00:27:13,880
Qian Fei.

529
00:27:13,960 --> 00:27:16,040
You have grown so chubby from love.

530
00:27:16,120 --> 00:27:17,240
I know

531
00:27:17,320 --> 00:27:19,280
you must have much gratitude deep within.

532
00:27:19,360 --> 00:27:21,240
Why not take the mic

533
00:27:21,320 --> 00:27:23,000
and say something to everyone?

534
00:27:24,080 --> 00:27:25,000
I…

535
00:27:25,640 --> 00:27:27,760
First of all, thank you for coming to my wedding.

536
00:27:27,840 --> 00:27:29,240
I never thought

537
00:27:29,320 --> 00:27:30,960
that I would get married so soon.

538
00:27:31,040 --> 00:27:32,200
I…

539
00:27:32,280 --> 00:27:33,560
I'm sure my buddies didn't expect

540
00:27:33,640 --> 00:27:35,360
that I would get married so soon either.

541
00:27:36,320 --> 00:27:38,000
I also want to thank my wife.

542
00:27:38,080 --> 00:27:39,840
My figure and height

543
00:27:39,920 --> 00:27:41,040
aren't a problem for her.

544
00:27:41,120 --> 00:27:42,640
Even someone like me

545
00:27:42,720 --> 00:27:44,600
can marry such a beautiful wife.

546
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:45,560
I…

547
00:27:47,480 --> 00:27:50,040
Guys, I've got a wife!

548
00:27:50,120 --> 00:27:51,440
Well done!

549
00:27:52,880 --> 00:27:54,400
Help me take a photo.

550
00:27:54,480 --> 00:27:55,560
All guests,

551
00:27:55,640 --> 00:27:58,600
let's raise our glasses!

552
00:28:00,840 --> 00:28:02,160
What are you doing?

553
00:28:02,240 --> 00:28:03,160
Raise your glasses.

554
00:28:03,240 --> 00:28:04,480
Yes, right! Raise our glasses.

555
00:28:04,560 --> 00:28:05,720
Buddies!

556
00:28:06,440 --> 00:28:07,640
Eat and drink your fill!

557
00:28:07,720 --> 00:28:08,600
Cheers!

558
00:28:08,680 --> 00:28:09,920
-All right! -Cheers!

559
00:28:10,000 --> 00:28:11,200
Let's count down from three

560
00:28:11,280 --> 00:28:12,720
and wish them a happy marriage!

561
00:28:12,800 --> 00:28:14,720
Three, two, one!

562
00:28:14,800 --> 00:28:17,880
-Have a happy marriage! -Have a happy marriage!

563
00:28:17,960 --> 00:28:19,320
Cheers!

564
00:28:21,520 --> 00:28:23,520
Okay, as we watch the lovely newlyweds

565
00:28:23,600 --> 00:28:24,760
leave the wedding stage,

566
00:28:24,840 --> 00:28:27,320
this marks the start

567
00:28:27,400 --> 00:28:31,040
of Qian Fei and Shiwen's wedding banquet!

568
00:28:31,120 --> 00:28:32,400
-Come on. -May all of you eat up

569
00:28:32,480 --> 00:28:35,040
-Let's dig in. -and become as chubby as Qian Fei!

570
00:28:35,120 --> 00:28:36,080
I want this one.

571
00:28:36,640 --> 00:28:38,040
It's so close to you.

572
00:28:38,120 --> 00:28:39,080
Fine.

573
00:28:39,720 --> 00:28:41,320
You can have

574
00:28:42,120 --> 00:28:43,080
all the corn.

575
00:28:43,160 --> 00:28:44,760
WHY DIDN'T YOU SAY HI?

576
00:28:44,840 --> 00:28:46,120
Are you happy now?

577
00:28:49,400 --> 00:28:51,080
I can't take it anymore.

578
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:54,280
BROTHER NO. 2

579
00:28:55,040 --> 00:28:56,360
Why didn't you say hi?

580
00:29:02,560 --> 00:29:03,680
Zhizhi,

581
00:29:03,760 --> 00:29:05,320
I bought you a chocolate cake.

582
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:06,280
It's in the fridge.

583
00:29:06,360 --> 00:29:07,440
Remember to eat it.

584
00:29:12,160 --> 00:29:13,520
It's not important.

585
00:29:18,080 --> 00:29:19,000
Who is Zhizhi?

586
00:29:22,800 --> 00:29:23,960
Like you don't know.

587
00:29:24,040 --> 00:29:24,920
It's my nickname.

588
00:29:25,640 --> 00:29:27,480
Why doesn't your brother call you that?

589
00:29:30,160 --> 00:29:32,080
He calls me that occasionally.

590
00:29:32,160 --> 00:29:33,160
When I don't tick him off.

591
00:29:33,240 --> 00:29:34,760
Who else calls you that?

592
00:29:36,840 --> 00:29:39,160
My dad, mom, aunt, uncle,

593
00:29:39,240 --> 00:29:40,280
and eldest aunt.

594
00:29:41,000 --> 00:29:43,200
Those who are close to me call me that.

595
00:29:52,520 --> 00:29:54,720
And what's up with "Brother No. 2"?

596
00:30:01,320 --> 00:30:03,040
Brother No. 1 and Brother No. 2.

597
00:30:03,520 --> 00:30:05,120
Is there a problem with that?

598
00:30:05,200 --> 00:30:06,800
Why am I your Brother No. 2?

599
00:30:08,000 --> 00:30:09,160
You're older than Sang Yan.

600
00:30:09,960 --> 00:30:11,120
So

601
00:30:12,240 --> 00:30:13,280
one and two.

602
00:30:18,440 --> 00:30:19,440
Fine.

603
00:30:27,240 --> 00:30:28,840
How old is the guy you like?

604
00:30:33,920 --> 00:30:35,920
Why is he bringing this up again?

605
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:37,200
Why do you care?

606
00:30:39,200 --> 00:30:40,160
Tell me.

607
00:30:40,680 --> 00:30:41,880
Is he in the same year

608
00:30:41,960 --> 00:30:43,520
and same school as you?

609
00:30:43,600 --> 00:30:44,440
No.

610
00:30:45,480 --> 00:30:46,840
Who else do you know?

611
00:30:49,000 --> 00:30:50,720
I know people outside of school too.

612
00:30:51,280 --> 00:30:52,480
How did you meet him?

613
00:30:53,040 --> 00:30:54,440
We met while we hung out.

614
00:30:54,520 --> 00:30:55,560
Where?

615
00:30:55,640 --> 00:30:57,400
A bar.

616
00:31:01,000 --> 00:31:02,040
That's not right.

617
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:05,280
When you were drunk, you told me

618
00:31:05,360 --> 00:31:06,520
that you met him at a KTV.

619
00:31:12,000 --> 00:31:14,000
Did I say that?

620
00:31:15,080 --> 00:31:16,600
What did I say?

621
00:31:18,800 --> 00:31:19,680
Yes.

622
00:31:20,560 --> 00:31:22,120
We met at a KTV.

623
00:31:22,200 --> 00:31:24,920
I've met a lot of people,

624
00:31:25,480 --> 00:31:26,360
so I got confused.

625
00:31:31,760 --> 00:31:32,680
What's wrong?

626
00:31:35,320 --> 00:31:36,320
Nothing.

627
00:31:37,920 --> 00:31:38,920
I just think

628
00:31:40,600 --> 00:31:41,840
that Qian Fei is quite smart.

629
00:31:44,400 --> 00:31:46,280
What does Qian Fei have to do with this?

630
00:31:55,240 --> 00:31:56,520
How did you fall for him?

631
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:59,280
Give me a break, please.

632
00:32:01,320 --> 00:32:02,440
Why should I tell you?

633
00:32:04,240 --> 00:32:05,520
-Look at him. -Let's switch seats.

634
00:32:06,800 --> 00:32:07,720
No, I don't want to.

635
00:32:07,800 --> 00:32:09,080
-You… -Sit over here.

636
00:32:09,160 --> 00:32:10,200
Just sit there.

637
00:32:11,280 --> 00:32:13,600
My darling brother, eat up. Have more.

638
00:32:14,520 --> 00:32:15,400
No way.

639
00:32:15,480 --> 00:32:16,920
You just sit there.

640
00:32:24,040 --> 00:32:27,680
WE'VE TIED THE KNOT, A HAPPY AND LASTING MARRIAGE

641
00:32:27,760 --> 00:32:29,000
Top it off.

642
00:32:29,080 --> 00:32:30,000
What does this mean?

643
00:32:30,560 --> 00:32:31,600
Are you not drinking?

644
00:32:31,680 --> 00:32:32,960
Is this how you respond

645
00:32:33,040 --> 00:32:34,720
to your challenge five years ago?

646
00:32:34,800 --> 00:32:36,760
Let me have a bite. Quickly.

647
00:32:36,840 --> 00:32:38,400
I'm starving.

648
00:32:38,480 --> 00:32:39,480
Here.

649
00:32:39,560 --> 00:32:40,800
-I'm so hungry. -Eat something.

650
00:32:40,880 --> 00:32:42,880
-Then we'll drink after this. -All right.

651
00:32:42,960 --> 00:32:44,200
Okay, don't worry.

652
00:32:44,760 --> 00:32:46,360
-No problem. -You didn't even take a sip.

653
00:32:46,440 --> 00:32:47,920
-I'll fill it up for you. -Okay.

654
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:48,880
Where is Qian Fei?

655
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:50,200
He's seeing the guests off.

656
00:32:50,760 --> 00:32:52,440
They're such a sweet couple.

657
00:32:52,520 --> 00:32:53,760
My goodness. I envy him so much.

658
00:32:53,840 --> 00:32:54,920
Envious?

659
00:32:56,240 --> 00:32:57,760
Lift your head. What's wrong?

660
00:32:59,120 --> 00:33:00,400
When are you leaving?

661
00:33:01,880 --> 00:33:03,640
I haven't seen them in a long time.

662
00:33:03,720 --> 00:33:06,000
-I want to drink with them. -Okay.

663
00:33:08,000 --> 00:33:10,160
Here. Let's drink until we drop.

664
00:33:11,160 --> 00:33:12,680
Sang Yan, give up.

665
00:33:12,760 --> 00:33:13,800
I'm heading home then.

666
00:33:13,880 --> 00:33:15,840
Sure. Go home first. Do you need a ride?

667
00:33:15,920 --> 00:33:17,440
No, I can go by myself.

668
00:33:17,520 --> 00:33:18,720
I really can't stand those two.

669
00:33:18,800 --> 00:33:20,280
-Good idea. -Okay.

670
00:33:20,360 --> 00:33:21,600
Come on, guys.

671
00:33:22,240 --> 00:33:23,120
Let's drink.

672
00:33:23,920 --> 00:33:25,680
Jiaxu, I'm heading home first.

673
00:33:25,760 --> 00:33:27,760
Here, a toast to you.

674
00:33:27,840 --> 00:33:29,480
I'm leaving, everyone.

675
00:33:29,560 --> 00:33:30,960
-Goodbye. -Bye, little demon.

676
00:33:31,720 --> 00:33:32,720
Be careful.

677
00:33:32,800 --> 00:33:33,760
Little demon.

678
00:33:35,120 --> 00:33:35,960
Bye.

679
00:33:36,040 --> 00:33:37,240
Don't drink too much.

680
00:33:37,320 --> 00:33:38,720
Don't worry. I'll take care of him.

681
00:33:41,280 --> 00:33:42,160
There he goes again.

682
00:33:55,240 --> 00:33:56,080
Sang Zhi.

683
00:33:57,800 --> 00:33:59,040
Why are you walking so fast?

684
00:34:00,320 --> 00:34:01,520
Are you leaving too?

685
00:34:02,320 --> 00:34:03,560
No.

686
00:34:03,640 --> 00:34:04,720
But it's late now.

687
00:34:04,800 --> 00:34:06,520
I'll drive you home in your brother's car.

688
00:34:06,600 --> 00:34:07,840
Didn't you drink…

689
00:34:10,360 --> 00:34:12,199
You were sitting next to me all night.

690
00:34:12,280 --> 00:34:13,560
Don't you know if I drank or not?

691
00:34:13,639 --> 00:34:14,960
I know you didn't.

692
00:34:15,040 --> 00:34:17,040
But you don't have to see me home.

693
00:34:17,120 --> 00:34:18,400
I can go back by myself.

694
00:34:18,960 --> 00:34:21,080
Driving back and forth is troublesome.

695
00:34:21,719 --> 00:34:22,639
Not at all.

696
00:34:24,760 --> 00:34:26,000
It might be troublesome

697
00:34:26,080 --> 00:34:27,040
if it were someone else.

698
00:34:36,920 --> 00:34:38,480
What? Are you giving it back to me?

699
00:34:39,960 --> 00:34:41,560
I'm returning the red packet

700
00:34:41,639 --> 00:34:42,880
to our Zhizhi.

701
00:34:47,440 --> 00:34:48,639
Wait.

702
00:34:48,719 --> 00:34:49,960
What did you just call me?

703
00:34:50,800 --> 00:34:51,639
Zhizhi.

704
00:34:52,480 --> 00:34:54,840
You said people close to you call you that.

705
00:35:00,680 --> 00:35:02,360
You should keep this.

706
00:35:03,280 --> 00:35:04,880
Since you've called Sang Yan…

707
00:35:05,800 --> 00:35:07,920
You should get something for that.

708
00:35:08,640 --> 00:35:10,440
It's for Zhizhi.

709
00:35:10,520 --> 00:35:11,600
It's no loss.

710
00:35:14,120 --> 00:35:15,040
Take it.

711
00:35:16,520 --> 00:35:17,400
Let's go.

712
00:35:31,120 --> 00:35:32,800
When are you returning to school?

713
00:35:32,880 --> 00:35:34,200
Tomorrow morning.

714
00:35:34,280 --> 00:35:35,200
What time?

715
00:35:35,680 --> 00:35:37,040
The flight is just after 8:00 a.m.

716
00:35:37,920 --> 00:35:39,120
We're on the same flight.

717
00:35:41,320 --> 00:35:42,520
Tomorrow morning,

718
00:35:42,600 --> 00:35:44,160
I'll come and take you to the airport.

719
00:35:55,160 --> 00:35:56,160
Thank you, Jiaxu.

720
00:36:48,600 --> 00:36:50,040
I'll go inside then.

721
00:36:57,880 --> 00:36:59,040
It's your New Year's gift.

722
00:37:03,320 --> 00:37:04,320
Thank you, Jiaxu.

723
00:37:05,560 --> 00:37:06,520
Open it.

724
00:37:41,360 --> 00:37:42,680
Are these my initials?

725
00:37:45,440 --> 00:37:46,360
Do you like it?

726
00:37:55,880 --> 00:37:56,840
Well…

727
00:38:02,920 --> 00:38:04,080
Go in and sleep soon.

728
00:38:06,280 --> 00:38:07,120
All right.

729
00:38:08,480 --> 00:38:09,320
Good night, Jiaxu.

730
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:13,920
Good night.

731
00:39:06,400 --> 00:39:08,760
A bracelet with my initials on it.

732
00:39:11,480 --> 00:39:12,440
What does that mean?

733
00:39:23,920 --> 00:39:26,440
What does a bracelet mean as a gift?

734
00:39:31,080 --> 00:39:32,560
"BRACELET" SOUNDS LIKE "CHERISHED LOVE"

735
00:39:32,640 --> 00:39:33,720
IT'S A GIFT FOR LOVERS

736
00:39:33,800 --> 00:39:34,880
Love?

737
00:39:57,480 --> 00:39:59,680
FRUIT FARM

738
00:39:59,760 --> 00:40:00,960
How much is this?

739
00:40:01,040 --> 00:40:02,080
Please scan here.

740
00:40:02,920 --> 00:40:03,760
Okay.

741
00:40:04,400 --> 00:40:05,600
It's done.

742
00:40:22,240 --> 00:40:23,160
Is it for me?

743
00:40:24,680 --> 00:40:25,920
You seem to like eating this.

744
00:40:34,160 --> 00:40:35,000
Let's go.

745
00:40:55,920 --> 00:40:57,200
Are you not eating it?

746
00:40:59,440 --> 00:41:00,440
Do you want one?

747
00:41:02,240 --> 00:41:03,160
I'll try it.

748
00:41:19,440 --> 00:41:20,520
Come closer.

749
00:41:23,600 --> 00:41:24,480
What?

750
00:41:24,560 --> 00:41:26,600
Do you want me to feed you?

751
00:41:46,880 --> 00:41:47,920
Sang Zhi.

752
00:41:50,360 --> 00:41:51,560
Watch yourself.

753
00:41:52,080 --> 00:41:53,840
Don't take advantage of me.

754
00:41:58,640 --> 00:41:59,720
You're shameless.

755
00:42:05,960 --> 00:42:07,120
UNKNOWN ARTIST - CAR MUSIC 6

756
00:42:07,200 --> 00:42:08,440
VOLUME
